hadiths[63]{hadithnumber,text}:
4154,Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke hum har aasani o tangi aur khushi o naakhushi mein aap ki baat sunengey aur itaat kerengey. aur hum haakim sey uski hukumat nahin chheenengey. aur hum haq par qaaim rahengey jahan bhi hon. aur kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat sey nahin darengey.
4155,Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baiat ki ke har aasani aur tangi mein aap ki baat sunengey aur itaat kerengey. aur baqi riwayat hasab saabiq zikr ki.
4156,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke hum har tangi o aasani aur har pasand o napasand mein aapki baat sunengey aur itaat kerengey. aur hum haakim sey uski hukumat key barey mein jhagda nahin kerengey. aur hum jahan bhi hon, haq par qaaim o daaim rahengey aur kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat sey nahin darengey."
4157,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke hum har tangi o aasani aur khushi o naakhushii mein aap ki baat sunen gey aur itaat kerengey, chahey dusron ko hum par tarjeeh di jaey. aur hum haakimon sey un ki hukumat nahin chheenengey. aur hum jahan bhi hun, haq baat dankey ki chot kahengey."
4158,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke hamney Rasool karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke hum apney tangi aur aasani aur apni pasand o napasand mein (aap ki) baat sunengey aur itaat kerengey. aur hum kisi sahibe-iqtidar sey uskey iqtidar key barey mein jhagda nahin kerengey. aur hum jahan bhi hon, adl o insaf par qaaim rahengey. aur Allah Taala (ki itaat) key barey mein kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat sey nahin darengey."
4159,"Hazrat Ubada bin waleed key dada mohtaram (Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke hum apni tangi o aasani aur apni pasand o napasand mein (har haal mein) aap ki baat sunen gey aur itaat kerengey, chahey dusron ko hum par tarjeeh di jaey. aur hum sahibane-iqtidar sey unka iqtidar nahin chheenengey. aur hum jahan kahin bhi hon, haq baat par qaaim rahengey. aur hum Allah Taala (ki itaat) key barey mein kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat ki parwa nahin kerengey۔ Shoba ney kaha : (حیث ما کان) key alfaz Sayyar ney zikr nahin kiye, Yahya ney zikr kiye hain. ( Sayyar ney sirf « وان نقول بالحق » key alfaz kahey hain. ) Shoba ney kaha : agar mainey is mein kuch ziyadti ki hai to wo Sayyar ya Yahya ki taraf sey hai."
4160,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (aey Abu-Hurera ! ) to apni pasand o napasand aur har tangi o aasani mein ameer ki itaat par karband rehna agar-che tujh par dusron ko tarjeeh di jaey.
4161,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki ke har musalman ki khair-khahi karunga.
4162,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki us baat par baiat ki ke aapki baat sununga aur manunga aur har musalman sey khair-khahi karunga.
4163,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baiat maut ( key alfaz ) par nahin ki thi, hamney sirf us baat ki baiat ki thi ke ( maidane-jang sey) bhagengey nahin."
4164,Hazrat Yazid bin abi Ubaid sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke Hudebiya key din tum (yani sahaba) ney kis baat par Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baiat ki thi? unhoney farmaya : maut par.
4165,Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main fateh Makka key din apney walid Hazrat Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid sey hijrat ki baiat ley lijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main un sey jihad ki baiat leta hun. hijrat to ab khatam ho chuki.
4166,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ird-gird sahaba kiram ki eik jamaat thi ke aap ney farmaya : mujh sey baiat karo ke Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraogey, chori nahin karogey, zina nahin karogey, apni aulad ko qatl nahin karogey, kisi par apni taraf sey ghad kar jhoot o bohtan nahin baandhogey aur kisi neki key kaam mein meri nafarmani nahin karogey, phir jo shakhs is ehad ko pura kerega, uska ajr o sawab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. aur tum mein sey jis shakhs ney un mein sey koi kaam kar liya aur us ko (duniya mein) uski saza mil gaee to wo saza uskey gunah ko mita degi. aur jis shakhs ney un mein sey koi kaam kya, phir Allah Taala ney uskey gunah par parda dal diya to us ka maamla Allah Taala key supurd hai, chahey maaf farmaey, chahey saza dey. Ahmed bin Saeed ney ( Ubaid Allah bin Saad ki ) mukhalifat ki hai."
4167,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum un kamon ki mujh sey baiat nahin kartey jinki aurton ney baiat ki hai? ke tum Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraogey, chori nahin karogey, zina nahin karogey, apni aulad ko qatl nahin karogey, kisi par apni taraf sey ghad kar bohtan nahin baandhogey aur kisi achey kaam mein meri nafarmani nahin karogey. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kyon nahin ? ( hum baiat karen ) phir hamney un kamon par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey baad jisney un mein sey koi kaam kya aur us ko saza mil gaee to wo saza uskey gunah ko mita degi aur jis ko ( duniya mein) saza na mili to uska mamla Allah Taala key supurd hai, chahey wo usey maaf farma dey, chahey saza dey."
4168,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga ke main aap sey hijrat par baiat karney aaya hun jabkey main apney maa baap ko rotaa chhod aaya hun. aap ney farmaya : unkey paas wapis ja aur jaisey tuney unhein rulaaya hai isi tarah unhein hansa.
4169,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey hijrat ki ijazat talab ki. aap ney farmaya : Allah tujh par reham karey ! hijrat bahut mushkil kaam hai. kya terey paas oont hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : kya to un ki Zakat deta hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : bastiyon sey bahar reh kar neki key kaam karta reh. yaqinan Allah Taala (hijrat na karney ki bina par) terey amal key sawab mein koi kami nahin kerega.
4170,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! hijrat kon si afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to un kamon ko chhod dey jinhein tera rab taala napasand farmata hai. neez Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hijrat do qism ki hoti hai. eik to shahri ki hijrat, dusri badwi (Erabi (dehati)) ki hijrat. badwi ka kaam ye hai ke jab usey bulaya jaey to wo aa jaey aur jab usey hukm diya jaey to wo itaat karey lekin shahri ko mashaqqat bhi ziyada hai aur sawab bhi."
4171,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma isliye muhaajir they ke unhoney mushrekin (aur unkey ilaqey) ko chhod diya tha. aur ansaar mein sey bhi kuch log muhaajir they kyonkey Madina bhi (aap ki tashrif aawrii sey pehley) shirk aur mushrekin ka ilaaqa tha, chunanche kuch ansaar Aqba ki raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ( Makka Mukarrama ) chaley aaye they."
4172,"Hazrat Abu Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey koi aisa kaam bataiye jis par main qaaim rahun aur usey jari rakhun. aap ney farmaya : hijrat kar. (is waqt, terey haq mein) iskey barabar koi aur kaam nahin."
4173,Hazrat Yaala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main fateh Makka key din apney walid mohtaram ko ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! merey walid sey hijrat ki baiat ley lijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main un sey jihad ki baiat leta hun. hijrat to ab khatam ho chuki hai.
4174,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! log kehtey hain ke muhajrin key ilawa koi shakhs jannat mein nahin jaeyga. aap ney farmaya : fateh Makka key baad ( Makka sey) hijrat ( ki koi zarurat ) nahin rahi lekin jihad karo aur niyat rakho ( agar kabhi hijrat karna padi to kerengey) aur jab tum sey jihad key liye nikalney ko kaha jaey to niklo.
4175,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din farmaya : ab ( Makka sey) hijrat karney ki zarurat nahin, albatta jihad karo aur niyat rakho. jab tum sey jihad key liye gharon sey nikalney ko kaha jaey to niklo."
4176,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad hijrat ki zarurat nahin rahi.
4177,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Waqdan Saadi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum eik wafad ki surat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. hum mein sey har shakhs aap sey koi na koi sawal karta tha. main sab key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. mainey arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! main apney peechey bahut sey log chhod aaya hun jo kehtey hain ke ab hijrat khatam ho chuki hai. aap ney farmaya : jab tak kuffar sey ladaai jari hai, hijrat khatam nahin ho sakti."
4178,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saadi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum eik wafad ki surat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. merey sathi (apni apni baari par) dakhil huye. aap ney unki matluba hajaten puri kin. main sab sey aakhir mein dakhil huwa. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kya kaam hai? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! hijrat kab khatam hogi? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tak kafiron sey ladaai jari hai, hijrat khatam nahin hogi."
4179,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey arz ki ke main aap sey baiat karta hun ke har pasand o napasand mein aapki baat sununga aur itaat karunga. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jareer! to uski taqat bhi rakhta hai? aur farmaya : to keh apni taqat key mutabiq. phir aap ney mujh sey baiat li aur farmaya ke har musalman ki khair-khahi karna.
4180,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki namaz qaaim kerney, zakat ada kerney, har musalman ki khair khahi karney aur mushrekin sey alehda rehney par."
4181,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. phir raawi ney sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kya.
4182,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa to aap logon sey baiat ley rahey they. mainey arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! apna haath badhaiye taake main aapki baiat karun. aur shartein aap khud bata dijiye kyonkey aap ziyada jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : main tujh sey baiat leta hun ke to ek Allah ki ibadat kerega, namaz qaaim kerega, Zakat ada kerega, har musalman ki khair-khahi kerega aur mushrekin sey juda rahega."
4183,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey chand logon key sath mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki. aap ney farmaya : main tum sey is shart par baiat leta hun ke tum Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek nahin banaogey, chori nahin karogey, zina nahin karogey, apni aulad ko qatl nahin karogey aur apni taraf sey ghad kar kisi par bohtan tarazi nahin karogey aur kisi nek kaam mein meri nafarmani nahin karogey. tum mein sey jo shakhs us ehad par qaaim raha, us ka ajr o sawab Allah Taala key zimmey hai aur jisney un mein sey koi kaam kar liya, phir us ko us kaam ki saza mil gaee to uska gunah dhul jaeyga. aur jis shakhs ki Allah Taala ney parda poshii ki, to wo Allah Taala key supurd hai. chahey usey azab dey, chahey to usey maaf farma dey."
4184,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke jab mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat karney ka irada kya to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! eik aurat ney daure-jahiliyat mein nauha karney mein madad ki thi. main ja kar uski madad kar key aati hun, phir aa kar aap ki baiat karungi. aap ney farmaya : ja, uski madad kar aa. main gaee aur mainey uski madad ka usey badla diya, phir main aai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki."
4185,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey baiat li ke hum nauha nahin kerengi.
4186,"Hazrat Umaima binte-Ruqeqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main kuch Ansari aurton key sath mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. hum aap sey baiat hona chahti thin. hamney arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum aap sey baiat karti hain ke hum Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek nahin banaeyngi , chori nahin kerengi , zina nahin kerengi , apni taraf sey jhoot ghad kar kisi par bohtan tarazi nahin kerengi aur kisi nek kaam mein aap ki nafarmani nahin kerengi. aap ney farmaya : apni taqat aur wusat key mutabiq ( tum paband hogi ). hamney kaha : Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum par ( hum sey bhi ) ziyada meharban aur reham farmaney waley hain. aey Allah key Rasool ! ijazat dijiye ki hum aap key daste-mubarak par baiat karen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main aurton sey haath nahin milaata. mera zabani taur par so aurton sey ( baiat ki ) baat cheet karna aisey hi hai jaisey har-har aurat sey alag taur par baat cheet karun."
4187,aale-Shareed key eik shakhs Amr key walid sey riwayat hai ke Banu Saqif key wafad main eik kodhi shakhs bhi aaya tha. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey pegham bheja : wapis chaley jaao (merey paas aaney ki zarurat nahin) mainey teri baiat qubul kar li hai.
4188,Hazrat Hirmas bin Ziyad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey (baiat key liye) apna haath Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf badhaya jabkey main us waqt ( nabaligh ) bacha tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey baiat nahin li.
4189,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik ghulam aaya aur us ney hijrat par Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat kar li. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ilm nahin tha ke wo ghulam hai. kuch der baad us ka Malik aa gaya, wo usey ley jana chahta tha. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ghulam mujhey bech dey. phir aap ney do kalay ghulam dey kar us ko kharida. uskey baad aap kisi sey baiat na letey yahan tak ke poochh letey : wo ghulam to nahin?"
4190,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key dast mubarak par qubul Islam ki baiat ki, phir us Erabi (dehati) ko Madina Munawra mein tap chadh gaya. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey meri baiat wapis farma dijiye . aap ney inkar kar diya, wo dobara aaya aur phir kehney laga : meri baiat wapis farma dijiye . aap ney phir inkar farmaya. aakhir wo Erabi (dehati) ( bula ijazat ) chala gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madina Munawra bhattii ki tarah hai. mail kuchail ko nikalta rehta hai aur khalis chiz ko baqi rakhta hai."
4191,Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) hujjaaj key paas tashrif ley gaey. us ney kaha : aey ibn Akwa ! tum murtad ho gaey ho aur eik kalma kaha jis key maana they ke ( Madina chhod kar) baadiya mein rehney lagey ho? unhoney farmaya : nahin balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey (apney baad ) baadiya mein rehney ki ijazat di thi.
4192,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat kya kartey they ke aap ki baat sunengey aur itaat kerengey. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmatey ke apni taqat key mutabiq .
4193,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke jab hum samaa-o-itaat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat kartey to aap hamen farmatey they ke tumhari taqat key mutabiq ."
4194,Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey samaa-o-aur itaat par Rasulullah ki baiat ki to aap ney mujhey (ye kehney ki ) talqin farmaai : apni taqat key mutabiq aur har musalman sey khair-khahi karunga.
4195,Hazrat Umaima binte-Ruqeqa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum chand aurton ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki. aap ney hamen farmaya : tumhari istataat aur taqat key mutabiq (ye baiat tum par laagu hogi).
4196,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abd Rabbe-Kaba sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas pahuncha. wo Kaba key saye mein bethey they aur log unkey ird-gird jama they. mainey unhein farmatey suna ke eik dafa hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath safar mein they. hum eik manzil mein utrey. hum mein sey koi shakhs abhi khema laga raha tha, koi (bator mashq) teer-andazi kar raha tha aur koi apney janweron ko charaney key liye nikal raha tha ke itney mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key manadi ney aelan kya : namaz key liye ikhattey ho jaao, chunanche hum sab ikhattey ho gaey. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur hamen khutba irshad farmaya. aap ney (khutba key doran mein) farmaya : jo bhi Nabi mujh sey pehley guzrey hain, un par zaroori tha ke apni ummat ki un baaton ki taraf rehnumai farmaain jinhein wo unkey liye behtar samajhtey they. aur unhein un chizon sey daraeyn jinhein wo unkey liye bura samajhtey they. aur tumhari is ummat ki khair o bhalai uskey ibtidaai logon mein rakh di gaee hai. baad mein aaney walon par badi aazmaaishein ayengi aur aisey halaat taari hongey jinhein wo napasand kerengey. be shumar fitney ayengey jo eik dusrey key muqabley mein halkey malum hongey. (eik sey badh kar eik hoga.) eik fitna aayega, momin samjhey ga ke ye mujhey halak kar dalega, phir wo fitna tal jaeyga aur uski jagah aur bada fitna aayega. momin kahega : ye halak karnewala hai (us sey to main bach hi nahin sakta ) phir wo bhi tal jaeyga, chunanche tum mein sey jo shakhs chahta hai ke usey aag sey bacha kar jannat mein dakhil kar diya jaey to us ko maut is haal mein aani chahiye ke wo Allah Taala aur youm aakhirat par yaqin rakhta ho aur logon key sath wohi sulook karey jo wo khud pasand karta hai ke merey sath kya jaey. jo shakhs kisi Imam ( ameer ) ki baiat kerey. uskey haath mein apna haath dey aur us sey dili taur par ( khulus ka) ehad karey to jahan tak ho sakey, wo uski itaat kerey. phir agar koi doosra shakhs (Muslima) ameer sey hukumat chheenney ki koshish karey to uski gardan maar do. ( raawi ney kaha : ) mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey qarib ho kar puchha : aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye sab baaten farmatey suna hai? unhoney farmaya : haan ! ( yaqinan )"
4197,"Hazrat Yahya bin Husein sey riwayat hai ke mainey apni daadi sey suna, wo farmati thin : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajjatul-wada mein farmatey suna : agar tum par eik habshi ghulam ameer bana diya jaey jo tumhein Allah Taala ki kitab (shariyate-Islamiya) key mutabiq chalaey to tum uski baat suno aur itaat karo."
4198,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney meri itaat ki, dar-haqiqat us ney Allah Taala ki itaat ki. aur jis shakhs ney meri nafarmani ki, us ney dar-haqiqat Allah Taala ki nafarmani ki. ( isi tarah ) jis shakhs ney merey muqarrar karda ameer ki itaat ki, us ney dar-haqiqat meri itaat ki aur jisney merey muqarrar karda ameer ki nafarmani ki, us ney dar-haqiqat meri nafarmani ki."
4199,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke ye aayat : « { یٰٓأَیُّہَا الَّذِیْنَ اٰمَنُوْٓا اَطِیْعُوا اللّٰہَ وَ اَطِیْعُوا الرَّسُوْلَ }  aey eman walo ! Allah Taala ki itaat karo aur Rasool ki itaat karo padhi. Hazrat Abdullah bin Huzafa bin Qais bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein utri. unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik lashkar mein (ameer bana kar) bheja tha.
4200,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jang do qism ki hoti hai. jo shakhs Allah Taala ki raza mandi ki niyat kerey. Imam ki itaat karey aur qeemti maal (jihad mein) sarf karey aur fasad sey bachey to uska sona jaagna sab uskey liye sawab ka zaria hain. lekin jo shakhs riyakari aur shohrat key liye ladaai kerey. Imam ki nafarmani karey aur zamin mein fasad phelaey , wo to pehli haalat mein bhi wapis nahin lotega."
4201,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imam dhaal hai. uski aad mein ladaa jaey aur uski madad key sath dushman sey bacha jaey. agar wo Allah Taala sey dartey huye hukm dey aur insaf karey to us ko us ka sawab milega aur agar wo is tarah hukm na dey to usey gunah hoga.
4202,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Deen to bas khulus o khair-khahi ka naam hai. sahaba ney arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis sey? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala sey, uski kitab sey, uskey Rasool sey, musalmanon key hukkaam sey aur logon sey."
4203,"Hazrat Tameem daari sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Deen to hai hi ikhlas ka naam. sahaba ney arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis key sath ikhlas? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key sath, uski kitab key sath, uskey Rasool key sath aur musalmanon key hukkaam key sath aur aam musalmanon key sath."
4204,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yaqinan Deen khair-khahi ko kehtey hain. bilashuba Deen khair-khahi ka naam hai. beshak Deen khair-khahi sey ibarat hai. sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis ki ( khair-khahi) aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ki, uski kitab ki, uskey Rasool ki, musalman haakimon ki aur aam musalmanon ki."
4205,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Deen khulus ka naam hai. sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis sey ( khulus . ) aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala sey, uski kitab sey, uskey Rasool sey, musalmanon key hukkaam aur riaayaa sey."
4206,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har haakim key Musheer do qism key hotey hain. eik musheer wo jo usey neki ka hukm deta hai aur burai sey rokta hai aur doosra musheer wo jo us ko kharab karney mein koi kasar nahin chhodta. jo haakim burey musheeron sey bach gaya, wo haqiqat mein bach gaya. aur us ka shumar un mein sey hoga jo is par ghalib aaye rahey."
4207,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney jo bhi Nabi bheja aur jisey bhi khalifa muqarrar farmaya, uskey do qism key musheer hotey hain. eik musheer usey neki ka hukm detey they aur dusrey musheer usey burai ka mashwara detey they aur burai ki targheeb dilaatey they. aur mehfooz wohi rehta hai jisey Allah Taala mehfooz rakhey."
4208,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo bhi Nabi maboos huye ya jo unkey baad khalifa baney, unkey musheer do qism key hotey they. eik musheer to in ko neki ka hukm detey they aur burai sey roktey they aur dusrey in ko kharab karney ki puri koshish kartey they. jo shakhs burey musheer sey bach gaya, wo haqiqat mein bach gaya."
4209,"Hazrat Qasim bin Muhammad sey riwayat hai ke mainey apni phuphi (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ) ko farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs kisi kaam ka zimmedaar baney, phir Allah Taala uskey liye behtari ka irada farmaai to uskey liye achcha wazir mohaiyya farma deta hai. jo us ko bhool janey ki surat mein uski zimmedari yad dilaata hai aur agar usey yad ho to uski (zimmedaari ki adaegi mein) madad karta hai."
4210,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik lashkar bheja aur un par eik aadmi ko ameer muqarrar farmaya. us ney aag jalaai aur kehney laga : is mein chhalangein laga do. kuch logon ney chhalangein laganey ka irada kar liya. dusrey kehney lagey : hum aag sey bachney key liye to musalman huye hain ( lihaza hum aag mein chhalang nahin lagaeyngey ). phir ( wapsi par) unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey us baat ka zikr kya to aap ney un logon ko, jinhoney chhalang laganey ka irada kya tha, ( mukhatib kar key) farmaya : agar tum aag mein chhalangein laga detey to qiyamat tak aag hi mein rehtey. aur dusron key liye khair ka kalma kaha. ( ustaad ) Abu-Musa ( Muhammad bin Musanna ) ney apni hadees mein kaha : aur aap ney dusrey logon key barey mein achi baat farmaai aur farmaya : Allah Taala ki nafarmani hoti ho to kisi ki itaat jayez nahin. sirf itaat achey kamon mein hai."
4211,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman shakhs par zaroori hai ke wo ameer ki baat suney aur uski itaat kerey. chahey pasand karta ho ya na. illa ye ke usey ( Allah aur uskey Rasool ki ) nafarmani aur gunah wala hukm diya jaey. aisi surat mein na wo ameer ki baat suney , na uski itaat kerey."
4212,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye. hum no sathi they. aap ney farmaya : merey baad kuch aisey ameer hongey ke jo shakhs unkey jhoot mein unki tasdeeq kerega aur unkey zulm mein un ki madad kerega to us ka mujh sey koi talluq nahin aur na us sey mera koi talluq hai. aur usey merey paas hoze-kausar par aana nasib nahin hoga. aur jo shakhs unkey jhoot mein un ki tasdeeq na karey aur unkey zulm mein unka sath na dey, wo mujh sey talluq rakhta hai aur main us sey talluq rakhta hun aur wo laziman merey paas hoz kausar par aayega."
4213,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye. hum no aadmi they. paanch arbi, chaar ajmi ya chaar Arbi aur paanch ajmi. aap ney farmaya : suno ! kya tum sun rahey ho? yaqinan merey (faut honey key) baad kuch aisey ameer hongey ke jo shakhs unkey paas jaeyga, phir unkey jhoot mein un ki tasdeeq kerega, aur unkey zulm mein unka sath dega , na us ka mujh sey talluq hai aur na mera us sey. aur wo merey paas hoz kausar par nahin aa sakeyga. aur jo shakhs unkey paas na gaya (ya gaya lekin) unkey jhoot ki tasdeeq na ki aur zulm mein unka sath na diya, wo mera hai. mein us ka hun aur wo zarur merey paas hoz kausar par haziri ki saadat hasil kerega."
4214,"Hazrat Tariq bin Shahab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha, jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apna paon mubarak rikaab mein rakh chukey they : kon sa jihad afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : zalim badshah key samney haq baat kehna."
4215,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum eik majlis mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. aap ney farmaya : mujh sey is par baiat karo ke tum Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek nahin thehraogey, chori nahin karogey. zina nahin karogey. (aap ney puri aayat tilawat farmaey) tum mein sey jo shakhs is ehad ko pura kerega, uska ajr o sawab Allah Taala key zimmey hai lekin jis shakhs ney un mein sey koi kaam kar liya aur Allah Taala ney is par parda dal diya to wo Allah Taala key ikhtiyar mein hai. chahey us ko azab dey, chahey maaf farmaey."
4216,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Raziallahu anhum ney farmaya : an qarib tum log amaarat (iqtidar o sardaari) ki hirs karogey aur bilashuba ye (qiyamat key din) nadaamat o sharmindagi aur hasrat o afsos (ka sabab) hogi. ye doodh pilaatey achi lagti hai magar doodh chhudaatey huye buri mehsus hoti hai. (uski ibtida (shuruat) achi malum hoti hai lekin anjam bura hoga.)
